---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Pembiayaan Semula Armada 2026',
  slug: 'pembiayaan-semula-armada-2026',
  excerpt: 'Refinance armada lama untuk dapat tunai. 0% deposit. Kelulusan pantas. Kurangkan bayaran bulanan.',
  date: '2026-01-17',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Pengembangan Armada',
  image: '/images/blog/fleet-refinance-2026.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['refinance armada', 'fleet refinance malaysia', '0% deposit', 'cash out'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/${lang}/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <header class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Pengembangan Armada</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
          <span>{post.author}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{post.readTime} min baca</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2>Refinance Armada – Dapat Tunai Pantas</h2>

        <p>Armada anda dah ada nilai. Gunakan nilai tu untuk dapatkan tunai. Boleh guna untuk bisnes baru, tambah armada, atau bayar hutang lain.</p>

        <h2>Kelebihan Refinance</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>Dapat tunai dari armada sedia ada</li>
          <li>Kurangkan bayaran bulanan</li>
          <li>Tukar high-interest loan ke lower rate</li>
          <li>Kelulusan dalam 24-48 jam</li>
          <li>Tiada had umur armada</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Bank vs Kami</h2>

        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: #D4A574;">
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Item</th>
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Bank</th>
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Kami</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Had Umur</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">5-7 tahun</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Tiada had</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Kelulusan</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">2-4 minggu</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>24-48 jam</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2>Cara Refinance Armada</h2>

        <ol style="list-style: decimal; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Hubungi kami – WhatsApp +60175700889</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Berikan detail armada anda</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Kami nilai armada anda</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Dapat offer dalam 24 jam</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Terima tunai dalam 48 jam</li>
        </ol>

        <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
          <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Nak Refinance Armada?</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">0% deposit. Tiada had umur. WhatsApp kami sekarang.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
        <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Pembiayaan Sekarang" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
      </footer>
    </article>
  </BaseLayout>

  <style>
    h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
    strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
    ul, ol { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
    li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
    ul li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
